title: Bosch Automotive Rear Wiper Blade H354 /3397011433 Original Equipment Replacement- 14 (Pack of 1), Black
description: Bosch is a manufacturer of wiper blades, using the same high quality standards - and many of the SKUs utilize the same design - as the Original Equipment blades. The rear wiper blades feature wear resistant natural rubber to ensure smooth and quiet operation as well as a specially coated wiping edge to contribute to long service life. Bosch now has a rear wiper blade to suit all requirements for the most popular domestic, Asian and European vehicles.
